node.text:
As seen at Monaco Yacht Club. Origin fuoco combines the finest Carrara marble with a customisable fire pit with remote control to create a powerful visual and tactile spectacle for the senses. Suitable for interior and exterior use. After a successful launch of Origin fuoco Studio Celiberti are delighted to launch Origin elettrica, a new cooking and dining experience in collaboration with Sub-Zero & Wolf. The Origin collection is bespoke and therefore can be customised to meet your requirements.
#studioceliberti #architects_need

node.text:
Once the rough components have been prepared in the machine room they are brought into our workshop where we turn tenons on the legs before planing them down to their final shape. Once the mortices have been drilled in the seats on the pillar drill we plane them smooth with a jack plane. The black stools have a textured top which is carved with a travisher and to aid with this we make these stools from tulip poplar as it carves much nicer than oak. 

The stools are assembled without glue and wedged from the top. As the oak stools are left raw and without any finish, cleaning up glue inevitably ends up looking messy and takes a lot of time. With tight fitting tenons and sturdy wedges the joints are extremely strong indeed without glue.

Once the feet have been levelled and chamfered the tulip stools are painted with three coats of black milk paint, then burnished with a scotch brite pad and finally treated with three coats of tung oil. 

This limited batch of stools is now for sale through our website with shipping available to the UK, EU and USA... link in @bibbingsandhensby’s bio.
#bibbingsandhensby #architects_need

node.title: From @bibbingsandhensby Making milking stools in oak and black milk paint.

Interested in seeing them in action?

node.text:
Welcome to the most desirable domicile on Barbados’ Platinum Coast. An exacting vision executed without compromise, this ultra-modern beachfront villa is designed, furnished and finished to perfection.
Architecture and environment come together in breath-taking fashion, from one of the world’s finest master suites, down to the fully equipped gym, past the Teppanyaki Bar and out onto the breathtaking golden beach. For anything else, our bespoke concierge service will ensure every other detail is just as perfect.
Check @diamantemglobalportfolio for a collection of the world’s most exclusive rental houses.
#alayavillabarbados #diamantem #architects_need

node.text:
The extra long bed frame and the ingeniously positioned headboard of the seemingly floating dream site. Thanks to its inclined position it is very comfortable if you want to read or watch TV in bed. But at the same time an additional surface is created behind the headboard which serves as a useful shelf for important things such as books, reading glasses and snuggle blanket. Available in natural treated solid wood: ash, beech, core beech, cherry, maple, oak, knotty oak, walnut, knotty walnut. In the SOMNIA bed – as in all other beds from vitamin design – health, design and material make a successful connection.
Tap here for more: https://www.modumshop.com/products/bed-somnia

node.title: Solid Wood Bed SOMNIA by @vitamin_design @gg_designart Shop @modumshop.de

node.text:
@l_atelier_paris might designed our favorite kitchen! How cool is it?
This gorgeous execution in the DC suburbs, bold use of color creating an outstanding balance of sophistication and warmth that is the foundation of French style.
Wire-brushed solid oak cabinets hand-painted in blue paired with our custom French range & hood in brushed stainless steel. 
“Dreams are made at home.”
All designed and hand made by L’Atelier Paris the world’s greatest kitchens, Check out them for more details and complete collection.
#l_atelier_paris #architects_need
